Input elements:

Button: On (restart if already on)
Button: Next
	if radio mode: next radio station
	if playlist mode: next song
Button: Next Album
	if radio mode: --
	if playlist: next album
Switch: Pause/Play
Switch: Radio/Playlist mode
Poti: Volume


[[Shutdown (Automatic if pause for at least 10 Minutes)]]

Output elements:
LED: Status On,
LED: Radio,



=>
GPIOS
4 Input
2 Output

Buttons: 3
Switches: 2
LEDS: 2


